f(x) = x^Tx, x \in R^n
(\alpha x + (1-\alpha)y)^T(\alpha x + (1-\alpha)y) \leq \alpha x^Tx + (1-\alpha)y^Ty
\alpha^2 x^Tx + 2\alpha(1-\alpha)x^Ty + (1-\alpha)^2y^Ty \leq \alpha x^Tx + (1-\alpha)y^Ty
\alpha^2 x^Tx \leq \alpha x^Tx
(1-\alpha)^2y^Ty \leq (1-\alpha)y^Ty
0 \leq\alpha \leq 1
2\alpha(1-\alpha)x^Ty
t\mapsto t^2
 (\alpha x + (1-\alpha)y)^T(\alpha x + (1-\alpha)y)=\alpha^2x^Tx+(1-\alpha)^2y^Ty+2\alpha(1-\alpha)x^Ty\leq\alpha^2x^Tx+(1-\alpha)^2y^Ty+2\alpha(1-\alpha)(x^Tx)^{1/2}(y^Ty)^{1/2}=(\alpha (x^Tx)^{1/2}+(1-\alpha)(y^Ty)^{1/2})^2\\ \leq\alpha x^Tx+(1-\alpha)y^Ty, 
\alpha^2 x^Tx + 2\alpha(1-\alpha)x^Ty + (1-\alpha)^2y^Ty \leq \alpha x^Tx + (1-\alpha)y^Ty
\alpha(\alpha-1) x^Tx + 2\alpha(1-\alpha)x^Ty + (1-\alpha)(1-\alpha-1)y^Ty \leq 0
 x^Tx - 2x^Ty + y^Ty \leq 0
